OL,3,CNearly #250k of taxpayer money spent
OL,4,Con HGV depot that can't actually house
OL,5,CHGVs
OL,7,FThe 35-year contract, which started in
OL,8,F2016, has so far cost the taxpayer
OL,9,Faround #2m.
OL,11,FThe earliest the council can break the
OL,12,Flease is 2031, when by then they would
OL,13,Fhave spent around #3.6m in total.
OL,15,FThe building has been used for storage
OL,16,Fof pandemic-related equipment, general
OL,17,Fstorage and was readied as an
OL,18,Femergency temporary morgue during the
OL,19,Fheight of Covid.
